customer_reviews.title: In his two years of life, my Golden Retriever ...
customer_reviews.text: In his two years of life, my Golden Retriever has been on a wide variety of foods including periods of prescription foods. Exams from my regular vet and three times from a specialist provided no answers for his bouts of vomiting and excessive diarrhea. Since he had been on ProPlan food for a while, I thought I would try their Grain Free foods. He's been on the wet and dry food for more than a month now and has had no issues and he loves the food. I gave a 4 star rating for the food but if this one proves to be the answer to his life long problem I'll will definitely add that 5th star.
customer_reviews.author: Suzanne

customer_reviews.title: Stella Approved
customer_reviews.text: Thank you to Purina for providing the best dog food the our senior pup had ever had. She enjoyed this for the entire last year of her life. It was easily eaten (she had very few teeth) and digested. It was the one time of day where she would get a little “pep in her step” and would run (sort of) when it was time to have dinner. We couldn’t have done it with out you, Purina Pro Plan, so thank you ❤️ We miss you, Stella ❤️

product_meta.title: Purina Pro Plan Grain Free Adult Canned Wet Dog Food
product_meta.description: Color:Beef & Venison| Size:(12) 13 oz. CansBe proactive and give your dog all the nutrients he needs when you feed him Purina Pro Plan SAVOR Grain Free Classic Beef & Venison adult wet dog food. Real beef as the #1 ingredient means this premium dog food is designed with your dog's health in mind. This meat provides protein he needs to maintain lean muscle mass. Each serving is free from corn, wheat or soy and has no artificial colors, flavors or preservatives. The high-protein formula delivers a wholesome meal with an exceptional taste to your dog's bowl, providing him with a delectable meal he is sure to enjoy. Knowing that your dog is happy gives you peace of mind with each feeding. Give your loyal friend a bowl of this tasty dog food in a dish by itself, or combine it with premium adult dry kibble from our SAVOR line, adding to the dish with delicious additional taste and texture.
